msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Haddii aad ka baxsan tahay Mareykanka, waxaan kugula talineynaa NOWPayments "
"(kharashka ugu hooseeya, tooska u socda wallet-kaaga). Haddii aad ku sugan "
"tahay Mareykanka, Stripe Crypto sidoo kale waa ikhtiyaar. Waxaad awood u "
"leedahay inaad adeegyo badan u dhisto oo aad booqdayaashu dooran karaan!"

