msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Bixinta Stripe Crypto (USDC) waxay kaliya ka jiraan ganacsiyada ku saleysan "
"Mareykanka. Haddii aad ka baxdo Mareykanka, Stripe kaliya aqbali doontaa "
"lacagta kaarka deynta ee ku jirta balansigaaga Stripe (ma ahan si toos ah u "
"crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Haddii aad ku sugan tahay Mareykanka, waxaad isticmaali kartaa Stripe si "
"toos ah u hesho crypto. Haddii aad ka baxdo, tixgeli NOWPayments ama "
"CoinGate si toos ah u bixiso crypto."

